1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"我認為可行<br />\n最起碼帶動到成個運動<br />\n羊群心理 人跳我又跳<br />\n終有一日大家都會唔撚拍卡直接跳<br />\n<br />\n再講 唔好彩比人捉到仲可以大條道理屌7返佢<br />\n因為你真係有拍過卡 check返佢就知7"},{"pid":"e96035df5b2cb57542ca79926ec42339758237ab","tid":1555648,"uid":159802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"再講多少少<br />\n跳閘唔單止係逃票咁簡單<br />\n係想用行為宣示對黨鐵近月行為的不滿<br />\n所以你拍完再跳 除咗令到唔敢跳的手足鼓起勇氣<br />\n同樣係一種控訴 <br />\n(當然你有信心唔俾人捉)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次<br />\n如果你單純想懲罰港鐡<br />\n用長者卡作用不大<br />\n因為據我所知 個筆錢係政府補貼"},{"pid":"b3586e0fc0f1d38a7a97948d4372431ac0cb6b24","tid":1555648,"uid":159802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:45:26.000Z","msg":"如果被人捉到正一正 跑都跑唔走<br />\n可以試下講<br />\n「睇cctv囉，你地831個段cctv交埋出黎」"},{"pid":"8908a06fafd93ac0abfdfb531a1c51109ee10d59","tid":1555648,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"[重要!] 全部入黎!! 跳閘前必睇注意事項!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556898</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求留言幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3d4d7d2016ba7ce85d37abdb82196d5f8499f26a","tid":1555648,"uid":7547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"黨鐵個個站擺10條友看住個閘，點會有得賺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802fe793a25472dad2b46bb78124725b5b65dec7","tid":1555648,"uid":261256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4d7d2016ba7ce85d37abdb82196d5f8499f26a","tid":1555648,"uid":7547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"黨鐵個個站擺10條友看住個閘，點會有得賺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile